<h2 id="swifty-postgresql">Swifty PostgreSQL</h2>

<p>Swifty PostgreSQL is PostgreSQL driver, written by Swift 3.0, run flawlessly in macOS 10.12.</p>

<p>The Swifty warpper PostgreSQLâ€™s pointer and C functions, and handle allocate/dellocate memory automatically.</p>

<p>Offer ability to connect many database simultaneously, modeling all PostgreSQLâ€™s enum and constants.</p>

<p>Field model adopt Presentable protocol, so you can get rawString or realData depend on kind of data eaiser, all expensive operations are lazy computed as well.</p>

<p>Itâ€™s also a small component in <a href="https://github.com/NghiaTranUIT/Titan-Postgresql">Titan app</a> (an PostgreSQL client).</p>

